Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.-01,0:00:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:01:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:38.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba"              "Nanohana"   "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having returned to the\NAlabasta Kingdom at long last,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi and Luffy's party\Nlanded at the port town of Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While hiding from\NBaroque Works' assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the group prepares for a trek across\Nthe desert to stop the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Luffy had rushed\Nahead of everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and found himself\Nlost outside of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Heroes' Reunion!\NHis Name is Fire Fist Ace!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youngster!\NI haven't seen you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time in Alabasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say? Check out\Nthis solid-gold apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is an incredible treasure\NI found in some ancient ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said one bite of this magic gold\Napple will let you live 1000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm not interested\Nin living a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to live today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A solid-gold apple?!\N--1000 years of life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?! For real?! You found\Nit in some ancient ruins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, sure did! It's a legendary\Nartifact of an ancient civilization!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bite and we can live 1000 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! It's the truth! I give you my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have very sharp eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll part with it for\Nthe one-time price of 1000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 Berries?! You got yourself a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't take him seriously if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to live 1000\Nyears for only 1000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit wasting time and look for Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done shopping,\Nso we leave for the next town
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the minute we find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Luffy run off to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a quick question.\NHave you seen this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be here in town. I've been\Nlooking for him for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Never seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if you're looking for someone,\Nask at the restaurant up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner there knows a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant, huh? I was\Njust feeling hungry, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that? He looks incredibly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he looking for Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a former pirate-hunter,\Nthere's no way I wouldn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selling a sword like this for 200,000\NBerries is as good as swindling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have a permit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were\NRoronoa Zoro, and a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rogue like you can't be\Nallowed to own a renowned sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll collect your sword,\Nthe legendary Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that woman doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never try this again!\NDo you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman spells nothing\Nbut trouble! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small fry pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought they could act\Nlike big-shots around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I took care of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in such a distant land, your\Ndistaste for pirates is unfaltering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got time for pointless chit-chat,\Nhave the royal army take 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be any word yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Straw Hat Luffy having\Ncome to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let your guard down.\NThey will show up. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker? That's the Navy\Ncaptain from Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he followed us\Nall the way here from Loguetown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's that man...\NThings could get ugly quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thanks for this lunch, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't enough at all one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world is the food place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It seems someone suddenly\Ndied in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He supposedly died in the middle\Nof a conversation with the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think he unwittingly ate a\NDesert Strawberry while traveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Desert Strawberry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're poisonous spiders that\Nlook like red strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat one by accident, and you'll\Nsuddenly keel over a few days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contagious poison spreads through\Nyour corpse a few hours after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so nobody can get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the desert, what you\Ndon't know can kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look! The way he's\Nstill stuck holding the meat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is proof of just how powerful\Nthe Desert Strawberry's poison is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's absurd! You were in the\Nmiddle of a conversation and a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's eating again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this commotion, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this restaurant do\Ncomedy skits or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that.\NBut it's good you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't sleep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, so he wasn't dead after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a false alarm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hit the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this guy been in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pirate who wears a straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're bold\Nenough to eat out in public...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Second Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgas D. Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whitebeard?! The Whitebeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dimwit is one of the\NWhitebeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I have seen\Nthe mark on his back before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mark of\Nthe Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a famous, big-shot\Npirate doing in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! There's a\Nweird smell in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's one! There's a food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To let me capture you quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy trying to find\Nanother pirate at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I have no\Ninterest in taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as I'm a marine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bland reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A food place! I finally found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can eat! I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy! Food! Food! Food!\NOn the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!\NFood! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! This is such a yum food place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. Thanks. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, you should probably\Nrun away while you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy that got sent flying\Njust now... Do you know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who sent someone flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did? Who went flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird shop!\NIs this your hobby, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caused it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry for disturbing your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiot would do\Nsomething this crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luf--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did come to Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here, Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you you can't enter\Nthe Grand Line unless you beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Plume-Plume Fruit.\NSo my body becomes smoke at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it? You can't even\Nenter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that smoke!\NWhat're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up! Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran off without paying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! My Gum-Gum moves\Ndon't work on that guy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do for now is run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Captain Smoker?!\NDo you want a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kingdom certainly is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch that guy! It's Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi! Gather the marines at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search every square inch of\Nthis town for Straw Hat's crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People with powers are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat's crew! That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro is in this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Why did you\Ncome to this kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I after? I'm here to\Nbeat up a guy named Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Crocodile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you and Crocodile connected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:18:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard thinks he's crafty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Luffy-san have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! He's always such\Na high-maintenance captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we'll be in big trouble\Nif we don't get moving quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a strange man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just find Luffy as quickly\Nas possible and leave town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What for?!\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a big commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him escape! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some idiot pirate must be\Nrunning around town or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that where you guys are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Go get rid of them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Straw Hat crew! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We have to run, obviously!\N--Hurry! To the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Let's get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Yikes! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Haze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be smoke, but I'm fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight between your power\Nand mine would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, anyways?!\NWhy is he helping us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?! Is that you, Ace?!\NYou ate a Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!\NWe're securing the perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, we can't chat like this!\NI'll catch up! You guys run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold these guys off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.\NWhy are you helping Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to\Nworry about his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Brother? You mean to say--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Portgas D. Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's a no-can-do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an acquaintance of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:22:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! This is my brother, Ace! Say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sensible man can't\Npossibly be your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've expected him to\Nbe as reckless as Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy who\Ncares about his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers can be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is just full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace and Luffy!\NHot Emotions and Brotherly Bonds"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
